{"tid":2005273,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[DW] 川普:疫情傷害超越珍珠港和911","createTime":"2020-05-07T04:04:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-07T04:13:46.000Z","uid":179729,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"024c8e68f44c478dd85aa6009a54e422b5fe8b82","tid":2005273,"uid":179729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T04:04:44.000Z","msg":"雖然美國各州本週陸續解除封鎖，但美國總統川普週三(5月6日)在例行記者會上也坦承，新冠疫情對美國造成的傷害已超越珍珠港事件丶二次大戰或是911恐怖攻擊事件。他說：「我們經歷了美國史上最嚴重的攻擊，我們真的做出非常多犧牲。疫情帶來的傷害，比珍珠港或是911恐怖攻擊事件所產生的傷害還大。」<br />\n<br />\n全文：<a href=\"https://p.dw.com/p/3bsMJ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp.dw.com%2Fp%2F3bsMJ&d=w9JnFmhD9tlFtzSpwKDBdZggdM0W6%2BkgeusliPwa7Y4%3D&h=b02d5d2e\" target=\"_blank\">https://p.dw.com/p/3bsMJ</a><br />\n<br />\nFacebook：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/dw.chinese.traditional/posts/876827472819897\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fdw.chinese.traditional%2Fposts%2F876827472819897&d=w9JnFmhD9tlFtzSpwKDBdZggdM0W6%2BkgeusliPwa7Y4%3D&h=a70a1e56\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/dw.chinese.traditional/posts/876827472819897</a><br />\n<br />\n咁樣講算唔算係為戰爭鋪路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3bc3c38865ceb15542ca4924f771bb2773558ca","tid":2005273,"uid":53515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T04:07:09.000Z","msg":"我都係咁解讀"},{"pid":"9328d8e36c0b00858b99c4f6c93a05db4ff79684","tid":2005273,"uid":51294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T04:09:24.000Z","msg":"用攻擊嚟形容<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"592b456428207dd0137f33578b98571e3ad87332","tid":2005273,"uid":179729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a3bc3c38865ceb15542ca4924f771bb2773558ca","tid":2005273,"uid":53515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T04:07:09.000Z","msg":"